item.title: Need SOMEONE TO HELP ME PORTFORWARD! Please!
item.dc:creator: @Samih1996 Samih1996
item.description:
@Samih1996 wrote:

Steps to portforward:

go to http://portforward.com/english/routers/port_forwarding/default.htm

there, search for the manufacturer name of your router, once you find it. you get directed to a page which has links on each model of the routers released from that manufacturer. Choose the model your router is. After that you will be directed to another page with lists of most games, look for “Runescape Private Server” and click on that.

Once you click it you will be directed to another page with all the steps on how to portforward.
